<paragraph blockId="56.[189,1091,313,340]" box="[189,1091,313,340]" pageId="56" pageNumber="57">The species is only known from the Knersvlakte and the Hantam Mountains.</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="56.[189,337,379,405]" box="[189,337,379,405]" pageId="56" pageNumber="57">
<heading bold="true" box="[189,337,379,405]" fontSize="11" level="3" pageId="56" pageNumber="57" reason="3">
